<div class="about-us-page">
  

    <main class="about-us-content">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p>Welcome to Manx Technology Recruitment Ltd, a leading recruitment agency based in the Isle of Man. We specialise in connecting talented professionals with innovative companies, helping both candidates and clients achieve their goals.</p>

        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>Founded in the heart of the Isle of Man, Manx Technology Recruitment Ltd was established out of a passion for technology and a commitment to excellence. With a deep understanding of the local market and a keen eye on global trends, we have become the preferred choice for tech professionals and companies seeking top talent.</p>

        <h2>Our Values</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Integrity</strong>: We operate with transparency and professionalism.</li>
            <li><strong>Excellence</strong>: We strive for the highest standards in our recruitment processes.</li>
            <li><strong>Innovation</strong>: We embrace new technologies and methodologies.</li>
            <li><strong>Community</strong>: We support the Isle of Man's work ecosystem and local talent.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Our Services</h2>
        <p>We offer a range of recruitment services tailored to meet the unique needs of the technology sector, including:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Permanent Placements</strong>: Matching skilled professionals with long-term career opportunities.</li>
            <li><strong>Executive Search</strong>: Identifying and recruiting top-level executives and leaders in the working industry.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Local Expertise</strong>: With a strong presence in the Isle of Man, we have an in-depth understanding of the local tech market and its dynamics.</li>
            <li><strong>Global Reach</strong>: Our extensive network allows us to connect with top tech talent and companies worldwide.</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Manx Technology Recruitment Ltd – Connecting Talent, Driving Innovation.</p>
    </main>
